title: ArcGIS Portal License
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: GPL
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors ArcGIS Portal license usage and expiration data.

 The summary service reports overall Portal member usage. Additional services are
 discovered for individual license items such as user types, apps, app bundles,
 and extensions when Portal returns those items.
item:
 The item is either summary or a license item in the form "<kind> <id>".
discovery:
 A summary service is always discovered when Portal license data is present.
 Additional services are discovered for license items returned by Portal.
perfdata:
 The check emits member usage, license usage percentage, and days until
 expiration when those values are available.
